| `deductSceneAwareCredit` | ✅ Safe | `usageTracking.js` |
| `addMusicCredits` | ✅ Fixed | `usageTracking.js` - added transaction + FOR UPDATE |
| `resetMusicCredits` | ✅ Fixed | `usageTracking.js` - added transaction + FOR UPDATE |

